WEBVTT

00:01.534 --> 00:04.051
Cheers is filmed
before a live studio audience.

00:04.120 --> 00:05.487
And I look up and I say,

00:05.554 --> 00:07.922
"It will never do,
it will never do."

00:07.990 --> 00:09.524
I just cannot believe...

00:09.592 --> 00:10.942
Normie.
Huh?

00:11.009 --> 00:13.311
Normie, it's the Kennedys.

00:13.312 --> 00:15.096
Let's go tell the
guys downstairs. No, no, no,

00:15.097 --> 00:16.164
I've got a camera with me.

00:16.165 --> 00:17.332
Here, quick, get a snapshot.

00:17.333 --> 00:18.433
I'll... I'll pretend
I'm with them.

00:18.434 --> 00:19.824
I'll be nonchalant, okay?

00:24.891 --> 00:26.641
Oh, would you guys
like a picture?

00:26.642 --> 00:28.109
Oh, that would be great-
do you mind?

00:28.110 --> 00:29.527
No, no.
You sure you don't mind?

00:29.528 --> 00:30.595
Great, thank you.

00:30.662 --> 00:31.712
Thank you.
Okay.

00:31.730 --> 00:33.364
(chuckling)

00:33.808 --> 00:35.734
That's great.
All right.

00:35.735 --> 00:36.785
Thank you so much.

00:36.786 --> 00:38.019
Thank you.
Appreciate it.

00:38.020 --> 00:39.590
Nice to see you.
Nice to meet you.

00:39.655 --> 00:40.705
Bye.
Yeah.

00:40.756 --> 00:41.806
Bye-bye.
All right!

00:41.858 --> 00:43.024
Hey!

00:47.847 --> 00:50.315
(theme song begins)

00:53.519 --> 00:55.820
♪ Making your way
in the world today ♪

00:55.888 --> 00:59.040
♪ Takes everything you've got ♪

00:59.108 --> 01:01.710
♪ Taking a break
from all your worries ♪

01:01.777 --> 01:05.129
♪ Sure would help a lot ♪

01:05.197 --> 01:09.083
♪ Wouldn't you like
to get away? ♪

01:10.319 --> 01:12.620
♪ Sometimes you want to go ♪

01:12.721 --> 01:16.741
♪ Where everybody
knows your name ♪

01:18.410 --> 01:22.813
♪ And they're always
glad you came ♪

01:22.881 --> 01:25.049
♪ You wanna be
where you can see ♪

01:25.117 --> 01:27.852
♪ Our troubles
are all the same ♪

01:27.919 --> 01:32.157
♪ You wanna be where
everybody knows your name ♪

01:33.392 --> 01:35.326
♪ You wanna go
where people know ♪

01:35.394 --> 01:38.563
♪ People are all the same ♪

01:38.631 --> 01:43.201
♪ You wanna go where
everybody knows your name. ♪

